<div class="about-me-section">
    <div class="about-content-wrapper">
        <div class="text-content">
            <div class="text-card">
                <h1 class="about-title">
                    Juan Pablo Riglos
                    <span class="role-badge">Full Stack Developer</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="about-paragraph">
                    Desarrollo aplicaciones web completas, desde el frontend con <span class="highlight">React y Next.js</span> hasta backends con <span class="highlight">Node.js y NestJS</span>. Actualmente estoy integrando IA en proyectos reales: un chat nutricional con <span class="highlight">LangGraph</span> que formará parte de mi e-commerce OhMyBox.
                </p>
                <p class="about-paragraph">
                    Mi proyecto más importante es <span class="highlight">OhMyBox</span>, un e-commerce de alimentos proteicos que desarrollé y mantengo en producción, usando Claude Code como herramienta para gestionar el desarrollo completo del producto.
                </p>
                <p class="about-quote">
                    <svg class="quote-icon" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
                    </svg>
                    Aprendo haciendo. Mi mejor forma de crecer es construir productos reales que resuelven problemas reales.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="image-content">
            <div class="image-wrapper">
                <div class="image-glow"></div>
                <img
                    class="about-image"
                    src="/misimagenes/conMate.jpg"
                    alt="Juan Pablo Riglos con mate"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
.about-me-section {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.2s;
}

.about-content-wrapper {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
}

/* Contenido de texto */
.text-content {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
}

.text-card {
    background: linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.4) 0%,
        rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.5) 100%
    );
    border: 1px solid rgba(75, 85, 99, 0.3);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
    position: relative;
}

.text-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        transparent,
        rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.2),
        transparent
    );
    -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
    -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
    mask-composite: exclude;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
}

.text-card:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
}

.text-card:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.5) 0%,
        rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.6) 100%
    );
    border-color: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

.about-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: rgba(229, 231, 235, 0.95);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
}

.role-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.15);
    color: rgb(251, 146, 60);
    border: 1px solid rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.3);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    width: fit-content;
}

.about-paragraph {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(229, 231, 235, 0.9);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
}

.highlight {
    color: rgb(251, 146, 60);
    font-weight: 600;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
}

.highlight::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -2px;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.4), transparent);
}

.about-quote {
    position: relative;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgb(251, 146, 60);
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0 0;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.05);
    border-left: 3px solid rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.5);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

.quote-icon {
    width: 1.5rem;
    height: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.3;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

/* Contenedor de imagen */
.image-content {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
}

.image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    width: 350px;
    height: 350px;
}

.image-glow {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -2px;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.3),
        rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3),
        rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.3)
    );
    background-size: 200% 200%;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
    animation: rotateGradient 3s linear infinite;
    filter: blur(8px);
}

.image-wrapper:hover .image-glow {
    opacity: 1;
}

.about-image {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
    transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    border: 2px solid rgba(75, 85, 99, 0.3);
}

.image-wrapper:hover .about-image {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: scale(1.02);
    border-color: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.4);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
}

/* Animaciones */
@keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
}

@keyframes rotateGradient {
    0% {
        background-position: 0% 50%;
    }
    50% {
        background-position: 100% 50%;
    }
    100% {
        background-position: 0% 50%;
    }
}

/* Responsive */
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .about-content-wrapper {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        align-items: center;
    }
}

@media (max-width: 1023px) {
    .about-content-wrapper {
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .image-wrapper {
        width: 300px;
        height: 300px;
    }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .text-card {
        padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .about-title {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .about-paragraph {
        font-size: 0.9375rem;
    }

    .about-quote {
        font-size: 1rem;
        padding: 1rem;
    }

    .image-wrapper {
        width: 280px;
        height: 280px;
    }
}

@media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about-content-wrapper {
        padding: 1rem 0.5rem;
    }

    .about-title {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .role-badge {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
    }

    .image-wrapper {
        width: 250px;
        height: 250px;
    }
}
</style>
